cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use Dork LLM, please cite it as below."
title: "Dork LLM: an end-to-end LLM systems platform (tiny GPT, evaluation harness, RAG + agents)"
abstract: >-
  A compact, local-first LLM systems project: a decoder-only transformer trained
  from scratch in PyTorch (with KV-cache inference and supervised fine-tuning), a
  reusable evaluation harness with CI gating, and a cited RAG + agentic research
  assistant, plus reproducible scaling studies and local experiment tracking.
  Educational-scale but engineered to a production bar.
type: software
authors:
